--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Basic sanity check tests
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

exposeDetector='mar'
exposeDetector='pe'
exposeDetector='atlas'

exposeDark(1, exposeDetector+'+exposeDark+1')
expose(1, exposeDetector+'+expose+1')
exposeN(1, 3, exposeDetector+'+expose+1+3')

* Check that dkphi can be moved before running these:
exposeRock(1, 1, exposeDetector+'+exposeRock+1+1')
exposeNRockN(1, 2, 1, 1, exposeDetector+'+exposeRock+1+2+1+1')

* Check that dx and dz can be moved before running these:
exposeGridAbs(1, -0.0256, -0.0356, 2, 0.8309, 0.8409, 2, exposeDetector+'+exposeGridAbs+1+2+2')
exposeRockLineAbs(1,1,dz,-8,-7,2,exposeDetector+'+exposeRockLineAbs+1+1+dz-8-7+2')
